'''羅納德·愛德華·桑托'''（{{lang-en|Ronald Edward Santo}}，{{bd|1940年|2月25日|2010年|12月3日|}}），為美國職棒大聯盟的三壘手。職棒生涯主要效力於小熊隊，<ref name="Ron Santo at Baseball Reference">{{Cite web |url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/s/santoro01.shtml?redir |title=Ron Santo at Baseball Reference |access-date=2021-03-06 |archive-date=2017-10-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171026164116/https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/s/santoro01.shtml?redir |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.baseball-almanac.com/players/player.php?p=santoro01 |title=Ron Santo at Baseball Almanac |access-date=2021-03-06 |archive-date=2018-09-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180918170726/http://www.baseball-almanac.com/players/player.php?p=santoro01 |dead-url=no }}</ref>最後於2012年入選名人堂。<ref>National Baseball Hall of Fame, Ron Santo [http://www.baseballhall.org/hof/santo-ron] {{Wayback|url=http://www.baseballhall.org/hof/santo-ron |date=20180103132227 }} Retrieved April 20, 2015</ref>

桑托的職業生涯一共入選9次明星賽，<ref name="Ron Santo at Baseball Reference"/><ref name="Ron Santo at the Baseball Hall of Fame">[http://web.baseballhalloffame.org/news/article.jsp?ymd=20081202&content_id=10281&vkey=hof_news Ron Santo at the Baseball Hall of Fame] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081212024401/http://web.baseballhalloffame.org/news/article.jsp?ymd=20081202&content_id=10281&vkey=hof_news |date=December 12, 2008 }}</ref>曾連續5年拿下金手套獎。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.rawlings.com/GoldGloveHistory.aspx |title=History: Rawlings Gold Glove Award |access-date=2021-03-06 |archive-date=2015-03-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150319230920/http://rawlings.com/GoldGloveHistory.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/awards/gold_glove_nl.shtml#multi |title=National League Gold Glove Award winners at Baseball Reference |access-date=2021-03-06 |archive-date=2019-05-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190528001941/https://www.baseball-reference.com/awards/gold_glove_nl.shtml#multi |dead-url=no }}</ref>他的10號球衣也被小熊隊給正式退休。1990年至2010年間，他都在播報小熊隊的比賽。<ref name="Ron Santo at the Baseball Library"/>

桑托在青少年時期就罹患糖尿病，不過他一直到1971年才公開此事。後來也因為病情惡化導致雙腿部分截肢。<ref name="Ron Santo at the Baseball Library">[http://www.baseballlibrary.com/ballplayers/player.php?name=Ron_Santo_1940 Ron Santo at the Baseball Library] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121019222310/http://www.baseballlibrary.com/ballplayers/player.php?name=Ron_Santo_1940 |date=October 19, 2012 }}</ref>
==職業生涯==
===芝加哥小熊===
1959年，桑托與小熊隊簽約，並於隔年登上大聯盟。<ref name=br>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/s/santoro01.shtml|title=Ron Santo Statistics and History|work=Baseball-Reference|access-date=December 3, 2010|archive-date=2021-04-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210425191339/https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/s/santoro01.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Ron Santo Trades and Transactions at Baseball Almanac">{{cite web |url=http://www.baseball-almanac.com/players/trades.php?p=santoro01 |title=Ron Santo Trades and Transactions at Baseball Almanac |publisher=Baseball-almanac.com |access-date=November 13, 2011 |archive-date=2020-10-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201017091107/https://www.baseball-almanac.com/players/trades.php?p=santoro01 |dead-url=no }}</ref>1961年，桑托在單季製造41次雙殺，寫下隊史新紀錄。1962年，他的單季助殺數來到332次，一樣寫下隊史新紀錄。隔年他更是將紀錄推高到372次，寫下活球年代新紀錄。<ref name="Ron Santo at the Baseball Page">{{cite web |url=http://www.thebaseballpage.com/players/santoro01.php |title=Ron Santo at The Baseball Page |publisher=Thebaseballpage.com |access-date=November 13, 2011 |archive-date=2011-09-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110928031727/http://www.thebaseballpage.com/players/santoro01.php |dead-url=no }}</ref>1967年，他在國聯MVP票選中拿下第四名。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/awards/awards_1967.shtml#NLmvp |title=1967 National League Most Valuable Player Award voting results at Baseball Almanac |publisher=Baseball-Reference.com |access-date=November 13, 2011 |archive-date=2010-02-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100212112836/http://www.baseball-reference.com/awards/awards_1967.shtml#NLmvp |dead-url=no }}</ref>

1964年，和桑托同梯進入大聯盟的隊友Ken Hubbs因為發生空難去世，年僅22歲。後來Hubbs的故事被拍成紀錄片，而桑托也有參與演出。

1969年，小熊隊在球季前中段幾乎都位居聯盟第一。不過卻在最後25場比賽吞下17敗，最終爆冷被大都會超車，無緣晉級世界大賽。<ref>{{cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=3SoDAAAAMBAJ&q=baseball+digest+ron+santo&pg=PA66|title=''Ron Santo: A Hall of Fame Plaque In His Future?'' by Bill Dray, Baseball Digest, July 1992, Vol. 51, No. 7, ISSN 0005-609X|access-date=November 13, 2011}}</ref>這年他的打擊率為2成89，並敲出29轟與生涯新高的123分打點。最終他在MVP票選拿下第五名。<ref name=br/><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/awards/awards_1969.shtml#NLmvp |title=1969 Most Valuable Player Award voting results at Baseball Reference |publisher=Baseball-Reference.com |access-date=November 13, 2011 |archive-date=2009-02-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090201085337/http://www.baseball-reference.com/awards/awards_1969.shtml#NLmvp |dead-url=no }}</ref>
===腳跟踢擊===
1969年6月22日，小熊隊靠著Jim Hickman9局下的再見2分砲贏球，<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/CHN/CHN196906221.shtml |title=June 22, 1969 Expos-Cubs box score at Baseball Reference |publisher=Baseball-Reference.com |date=June 22, 1969 |access-date=November 13, 2011 |archive-date=2020-12-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201218073111/https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/CHN/CHN196906221.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>桑托在興奮之餘做了一個雙腳腳跟在跳躍時互相碰觸的動作，<ref name="Ron Santo at the Baseball Library"/><ref name="Ron Santo at the Baseball Page"/>並且連做三次。<ref name="Ron Santo at the Baseball Page"/><ref name=autogenerated1>{{cite web |url=http://www.baseballlibrary.com/ballplayers/player.php?name=Ron_Santo_1940 |title=Ron Santo at the Baseball Library |publisher=Baseballlibrary.com |date=June 26, 1960 |access-date=November 13, 2011|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121019222310/http://www.baseballlibrary.com/ballplayers/player.php?name=Ron_Santo_1940 |archive-date=October 19, 2012 }}</ref>
[[File:Ron_Santo_1969.jpg|alt=]]
隔天，總教練[[里歐·德羅許爾|里歐·德羅許爾]]認為他這個動作有助於鼓舞球隊士氣，因此要求他每當球隊贏球一定要秀出這個招牌動作。然而此舉卻惹惱了其他球隊，桑托也被認為是一名自大的球員，頓時成為聯盟最不受歡迎的球員。後來球隊在9月份吞下一波連敗，而桑托在9月2日球隊贏球做了這個動作後，便表示將不在觀眾面對表演這個動作。後來一直到2012年桑托入選名人堂後，小熊隊全隊球員在賽前才又復刻了這個動作向他致敬。

===拒絕交易===
當時大聯盟有一條條款叫做10-5條款，意思是當一名球員在大聯盟待滿超過10個球季，且在同一隊待超過5年的話，球隊需要經過他的同意才可將他交易。<ref name="santo2whitesox">[https://www.nytimes.com/1973/12/12/archives/santo-stays-in-chicago-cubs-trade-him-to-white-sox.html "Santo Stays in Chicago, Cubs Trade Him to White Sox," ''United Press International'' (UPI), Tuesday, December 11, 1973.] {{Wayback|url=https://www.nytimes.com/1973/12/12/archives/santo-stays-in-chicago-cubs-trade-him-to-white-sox.html |date=20201102092733 }} Retrieved October 30, 2020</ref>當時球隊原本要將他交易至天使，試圖換來Andy Hassler和Bruce Heinbechner兩名投手，<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/minors/player.cgi?id=heinbe001bru |title=存档副本 |access-date=2021-03-06 |archive-date=2015-03-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150322064154/http://www.baseball-reference.com/minors/player.cgi?id=heinbe001bru |dead-url=no }}</ref>不過卻被桑托給拒絕了。<ref name="santo2whitesox"/><ref>[https://www.nytimes.com/1973/12/09/archives/marichal-sold-to-red-sox-angels-fail-to-woo-santo-again-cards.html "Angels Fail to Woo Santo Again," ''The Associated Press'' (AP), Saturday, December 8, 1973.] {{Wayback|url=https://www.nytimes.com/1973/12/09/archives/marichal-sold-to-red-sox-angels-fail-to-woo-santo-again-cards.html |date=20201102103442 }} Retrieved October 30, 2020</ref>
===芝加哥白襪===
1973年12月18日，小熊隊最終還是成功將桑托交易至白襪，換來Steve Swisher、Steve Stone、Ken Frailing和Jim Kremmel。<ref name="santo2whitesox"/><ref>[https://www.nytimes.com/1973/12/19/archives/white-sox-finish-trade-for-santo.html "White Sox Finish Trade for Santo," ''United Press International'' (UPI), Tuesday, December 18, 1973.] {{Wayback|url=https://www.nytimes.com/1973/12/19/archives/white-sox-finish-trade-for-santo.html |date=20201102092742 }} Retrieved October 30, 2020</ref>由於球隊已有Bill Melton擔任三壘手，因此桑托多半時間擔任替補。儘管桑托多次向總教練提出想上場守備，不過他卻不願意將Melton降為替補選手。最後桑托還短暫守過二壘，整年他的打擊率僅2成21，而他在球季結束後選擇退休。<ref name=br/>
==名人堂票選==
桑托自1980年起便具有名人堂資格票選，不過他一直到1998年最高只有43.1%的得票率。

在票選資格被移除後，名人堂資深委員會多次將他提名到名人堂補選，可惜他都差了幾票未能入選。

2012年，黃金世代委員會將8位球員和2位執行長納入名人堂補選資格，而桑托在這次票選終於成功進入名人堂，而且是該屆唯一一位入選者。<ref>National Baseball Hall of Fame, Eras: Golden, "Rules For election For Managers, Umpires, Executives And Players For Golden Era Candidates To The National Baseball Hall Of Fame" {{cite web |url=http://www.baseballhall.org/hall-famers/rules-election/eras-golden |title=Archived copy |access-date=2013-04-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130430052048/http://baseballhall.org/hall-famers/rules-election/eras-golden |archive-date=April 30, 2013}}</ref><ref name="Ron Santo Elected to Hall of Fame">{{cite web|url=http://baseballhall.org/news/press-releases/ron-santo-elected-national-baseball-hall-fame-golden-era-committee|title=Ron Santo Elected to Hall of Fame|access-date=December 5, 2011|archive-date=2012-01-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120107222940/http://baseballhall.org/news/press-releases/ron-santo-elected-national-baseball-hall-fame-golden-era-committee|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=SomewhereACub/><ref>National Baseball Hall of Fame, November 3, 2011, "Ten Named to Golden Era Ballot for Baseball (1947 to 1972) Hall of Fame Election"[http://www.baseballhall.org/news/press-releases/ten-named-golden-era-ballot-baseball-hall-fame-election] {{Wayback|url=http://www.baseballhall.org/news/press-releases/ten-named-golden-era-ballot-baseball-hall-fame-election |date=20210126060038 }}</ref> 
==個人生活==
桑托很早就罹患糖尿病，不過為了延續他的職棒生涯而選擇隱瞞此事實。桑托會在比賽中以情緒來評斷自己的血糖含量，<ref name="thisoldcub">{{cite video | people = Santo, Jeff | title = ''This Old Cub'' | medium = DVD | publisher = Sony Pictures Home Entertainment | url = https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0408261/ | date = 2004 | access-date = 2021-03-06 | archive-date = 2021-03-08 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210308085436/https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0408261/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>當發現血糖過低時，他就會在休息室吃一些糖果增加血糖。<ref name="thisoldcub"/>不過最後他的雙腳仍在2001年與2002年因為病情惡化遭到切除。

2004年，桑托的兒子傑夫將其父親的事蹟拍成紀錄片《一位資深的小熊球員》(This Old Cub)。<ref name=SomewhereACub>{{cite web|first=Phil|last=Taylor|title=Somewhere A Cub Is Smiling|date=December 19, 2011|work=Sports Illustrated|url=http://sportsillustrated.cnn.com/vault/article/magazine/MAG1193034/index.htm|access-date=2011-12-19|archive-date=2014-01-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140111005919/http://sportsillustrated.cnn.com/vault/article/magazine/MAG1193034/index.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Santo elected to Hall of Fame by veterans panel|url=https://news.yahoo.com/santo-elected-hall-fame-veterans-panel-161651046.html|author=Walker, B.|publisher=[[Yahoo!|Yahoo!]]|access-date=2011-12-05|archive-date=2016-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305034513/http://news.yahoo.com/santo-elected-hall-fame-veterans-panel-161651046.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2010年12月1日，桑托陷入昏迷。<ref>{{cite web|title=Beloved Cubs icon Santo dies at age 70|url=http://newyork.yankees.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20101203&content_id=16246292&vkey=news_mlb&c_id=mlb|date=December 4, 2010|access-date=2010-12-04|first=Adam|last=McCalvy|work=MLB.com|archive-date=2013-04-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130402170439/http://newyork.yankees.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20101203&content_id=16246292&vkey=news_mlb&c_id=mlb|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Report: Ron Santo dead at 70">{{cite web |url=http://www.chicagotribune.com/sports/baseball/cubs/chi-ron-santo-chicago-cubs-obit,0,1699814.story |title=Chicago Tribune |date=December 3, 2010 |access-date=November 13, 2011 |archive-date=2010-12-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101205233945/http://www.chicagotribune.com/sports/baseball/cubs/chi-ron-santo-chicago-cubs-obit,0,1699814.story |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://iknowjack.radio.com/2010/12/03/legendary-chicago-cub-cubs-radio-broadcaster-ron-santo-dies/ |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101207140020/http://iknowjack.radio.com/2010/12/03/legendary-chicago-cub-cubs-radio-broadcaster-ron-santo-dies/ |archive-date=December 7, 2010 |title=Remembering Ron Santo (1940–2010) |publisher=Iknowjack.radio.com |date=December 3, 2010 |access-date=November 13, 2011 }}</ref>
<ref>{{cite web |url=http://us99country.radio.com/2010/12/03/from-the-north-side-to-the-south-chicago-loses-a-sports-legend/ |title=From The North Side To The South Side, Chicago Loses A Sports Legend |publisher=Us99country.radio.com |date=December 3, 2010 |access-date=November 13, 2011 |archive-date=2012-03-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120313052020/http://us99country.radio.com/2010/12/03/from-the-north-side-to-the-south-chicago-loses-a-sports-legend/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>兩天後他因為膀胱癌和糖尿病引發的併發症去世，享年70歲。<ref name="Rozner">{{cite news|url=http://www.dailyherald.com/article/20101224/sports/712259923/|title=Ron Santo's last gift to his family|last=Rozner|first=Barry|date=December 24, 2010|work=dailyherald.com|access-date=January 2, 2011|archive-date=2021-01-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210122010018/https://www.dailyherald.com/article/20101224/sports/712259923/|dead-url=no}}</ref>2011年8月10日，小熊隊在主場旁邊設置了一座桑托的塑像，以紀念他的貢獻。
